Andrew Kevin Walker -LRB- born August 14 , 1964 -RRB- is an American BAFTA-nominated screenwriter .
He is known for having written Seven -LRB- 1995 -RRB- , for which he earned a nomination for the BAFTA Award for Best Original Screenplay , as well as several other films , including 8mm -LRB- 1999 -RRB- , Sleepy Hollow -LRB- 1999 -RRB- and many uncredited script rewrites .